      <title>日本学生在中国遭刺伤，袭击事件再添新篇章</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japanese-student-stabbed-in-china-adding-to-spate-of-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名日本学生周三在深圳被刺伤，这是中国近几个月发生的一系列持刀袭击事件之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japanese-student-stabbed-in-china-adding-to-spate-of-attacks</guid>
